  ${
    pjsdi2.1 $e |- H e. CH $.
    pjsdi2.2 $e |- R : H~ --> H~ $.
    pjsdi2.3 $e |- S : H~ --> H~ $.
    pjsdi2.4 $e |- T : H~ --> H~ $.
    $( Chained distributive law for Hilbert space operator difference. $)
    pjsdi2 $p |- ( ( R o. ( S +op T ) ) =
                ( ( R o. S ) +op ( R o. T ) ) ->
           ( ( ( proj ` H ) o. R ) o. ( S +op T ) ) =
