  ${
    $d x y H $.  $d x y G $.
    pjco.1 $e |- G e. CH $.
    pjco.2 $e |- H e. CH $.
    $( Composition of projections. $)
    pjco $p |- ( A e. H~ -> ( ( ( proj ` G ) o. ( proj ` H ) ) ` A ) =
               ( ( proj ` G ) ` ( ( proj ` H ) ` A ) ) ) $=
      ( cpj cfv pjf hoco ) ABFGCFGBDHCEHI $.
      $( [16-Aug-2000] $)

    $( Closure of composition of projections. $)
